#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kate.1.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kate</command> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-s, --start</option> "
"<replaceable> name</replaceable> </group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>--"
