"group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-b, --block</option></group> <group "
"choice=\"opt\"><option>-p, --pid</option><replaceable> المعرف</replaceable></"
"group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-e, --encoding</option> <replaceable> "
